er` to `registerUser` in core's `user.ts` and `index.ts`, but two call sites still use the old name `createUser`.\n\n**Step 1: Fix api/src/routes/users.ts**\n\nChange import from `createUser` to `registerUser` (line 7), and change the usage on line 63 from `createUser(req.body)` to `registerUser(req.body)`.\n\n**Step 2: Fix worker/src/jobs/sync.ts**\n\nChange import from `createUser` to `registerUser` (line 7), and change the usage on line 48 from `createUser(input)` to `registerUser(input)`.\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Fix Root tsconfig.json Project References Build Order\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `/workspace/tsconfig.json`\n\n**Problem:** The root tsconfig lists packages in wrong order: api, worker, core. But core has no dependencies, while api and worker both depend on core. The correct order is core first.\n\n**Step 1: Reorder references**\n\nChange from:\n```json\n{\n  \"files\": [],\n  \"references\": [\n    { \"path\": \"packages/api\" },\n    { \"path\": \"packages/worker\" },\n    { \"path\": \"packages/core\" }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nTo:\n```json\n{\n  \"files\": [],\n  \"references\": [\n    { \"path\": \"packages/core\" },\n    { \"path\": \"packages/api\" },\n    { \"path\": \"packages/worker\" }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Fix Zod Dependency Version\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `/workspace/packages/core/package.json`\n\n**Problem:** zod is pinned to `3.19.0` but the code uses `z.pipe()` which requires zod >= 3.22.\n\n**Step 1: Update zod version**\n\nChange `\"zod\": \"3.19.0\"` to `\"zod\": \"^3.23.0\"` in `/workspace/packages/core/package.json`.\n\n**Step 2: Reinstall dependencies**\n\nRun: `npm install`\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: Resolve Merge Conflict Markers\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `/workspace/packages/api/tests/users.test.ts`\n\n**Problem:** Lines 22-36 contain unresolved merge conflict markers. The \"refactor\" branch version is correct since `registerUser` requires a `role` field.\n\n**Step 1: Resolve the conflict**\n\nKeep the refactor branch version (the on